name: Air Jordan 1 OG Dior Sneakers
description: On June 25, Dior launched a dedicated microsite at capsule.dior.com for the Air Jordan 1 by Dior drop. There, customers had an opportunity to buy the limited-edition shoes on a first-come, first-served basis. The shoes are priced at $2,000 for the low-top version and $2,200 for the high-top model.

name: Nike Air Max 97 Gold Bullet
description: When it comes to iconic colourways, you'd be hard pressed to find one as legendary as the Nike Air Max 97 Gold Bullet. An offshoot of Christian Tresser's Silver Bullet which was introduced 25 years ago, the Gold Bullet shot into the sneakersphere just two years later. Last seen in 2017, the mythical sneaker will be returning once again in 2023, so if you didn't manage to secure your size a few years back then you need to keep it locked at The Sole Supplier's dedicated page!

name: B22 SNEAKER
description: The B22 sneaker reimagines the chunky sneaker through a retro lens. Combining different materials and textures, including pink and black smooth calfskin and pink and white technical mesh, it has a bold, sports-inspired aesthetic. Round laces and a raised Dior signature on the side complement the thick, greige sculpted rubber sole with black edging. The sneaker can be worn with any casual piece for a sporty and contemporary silhouette.

name: B31 RUNNER SNEAKER
description: As seen at the Dior Men Summer 2023 fashion show, the season's new low-top B31 Runner shoe is distinguished by its modern silhouette that combines technical expertise with the House's couture spirit. Crafted in white technical mesh, it is enhanced by gray Warped Cannage injected rubber in a futuristic new take on the House's iconic motif. The Dior signature adorns the tongue and front, while eyelets recall a hiking shoe and the CD Diamond drawstring cord accentuate the

name: DIOR OBLIQUE BLOUSON
description: The ribbed knit blouson reimagines an essential wardrobe item in a couture variation. Crafted in anthracite gray wool, it is distinguished by a tonal Dior Oblique motif quilted technical jacquard section on the front. It features a stand collar, zipped closure and drawstring cord at the hem. The hybrid blouson can we worn with any mid-season casual attire or under a coat in winter.

name: BLOUSON
description: The blouson offers a contemporary lens on outerwear. Crafted in beige linen and cotton blend jersey with pink, orange and blue checkered jacquard, it is accented by a Christian Dior Couture label on the cuff and contrasting fabric at the shoulders. The innovative and practical silhouette features multiple pockets including an interior phone pocket and a pocket with a grosgrain strap to attach a keychain. A stand collar and fold-away hood add a functional touch. Comfortable and utilitarian at the same time, the blouson will complete any of the season's outfits.

name: DIOR AND DUNCAN GRANT
description: The anorak is part of the DIOR AND DUNCAN GRANT AND CHARLESTON collection. The modern quilted silhouette is crafted in reflective fabric with an all-over multicolor print. Ribbed finishes, a signature technical zip at the neckline and tabs at the wrist offer unparalleled comfort and fit. The anorak can lend a modern touch to relaxed looks.

name: CHRISTIAN DIOR COUTURE REVERSIBLE HOODED TRACK JACKET
description: The hooded track jacket is revisited in a versatile reversible variation. Crafted in black cotton fleece, it is accented by a tonal Christian Dior Couture embroidery on the back, while the reverse is embellished with the House's hallmark Dior Oblique jacquard. Featuring a classic kangaroo pocket, the hooded zipped jacket will complete any sportswear or relaxed look all year long.

name: SADDLE BACKPACK
description: The Saddle backpack offers a modern and original take on the Saddle design. The black grained calfskin with contrasting topstitching is embellished with a 'DIOR' signature on the front. The spacious design has a compartment to hold all the essentials, while the flap Saddle pocket on the front and two side flap pockets offer easy access to a wallet, keys, headphones or phone. The practical backpack will lend the finishing touch to any outfit.

name: DIOR HIT THE ROAD BACKPACK
description: The Dior Hit The Road Backpack is a new style this season that combines modernity with the House's couture spirit. Crafted in black CD Diamond canvas inspired by the House's archives, it is embellished with smooth calfskin details. Adorned with two 'CHRISTIAN DIOR' nylon jacquard bands, the design has a spacious main compartment, a large flap pocket on the front and two flap pockets on the sides. The practical backpack will lend the finishing touch to all casual outfits.

name: MOTION BACKPACK
description: The Motion backpack is a clever hybrid accessory. It has a streamlined and modern design, while the black Dior Oblique Mirage technical fabric lends a sophisticated touch. Adorned with black grained calfskin, it features a spacious and practical interior. The bag has a top handle and two adjustable padded straps to wear it two different ways, thus rendering it both practical and elegant.

name: DIOR EXPLORER BACKPACK
description: DESCRIPTION Part of the Dior Ski Capsule collection, the backpack enhances the Dior Explorer line with a functional creation in a couture spirit. Crafted in black CD Diamond Mirage Ski Capsule nylon, it is distinguished by a CD Diamond signature rubber patch on the front. The spacious main compartment is completed by a front flap pocket with a Dior buckle, as well as two side pockets. Featuring padded straps and a ring allowing the attachment of keys or a D-Touch pouch, the backpack will lend the finishing touch to any casual outfit.

name: ERL NECKLACE
description: Part of the exclusive DIOR BY ERL collaboration, the thick chain link necklace in antique gold-finish brass reveals Christian Dior and ERL lettering. The necklace can be paired with other DIOR BY ERL creations to complete the look.

name: COUTURE CHAIN LINK NECKLACE
description: The necklace is a timeless creation with bold appeal. Inspired by the design of a chain bracelet, the thick silver-finish brass links reveal a Christian Dior Couture signature plate for a hallmark touch. An adjustable clasp also enhanced by an openwork CD Icon signature allows it to be worn at several lengths. The necklace can be coordinated with the bracelet and ring to complete the look.

name: CD DIAMOND THIN CHAIN LINK NECKLACE
description: The necklace pays tribute to an iconic code from men's collections in a contemporary creation. The thin silver-finish brass links reveal a modern silhouette punctuated with CD Diamond signatures in black resin. An adjustable clasp is also adorned with an openwork CD Icon signature, allowing it to be worn at different lengths. The necklace can be paired with other CD Diamond creations from the collection to complete the look.

name: DIOR BY ERL NECKLACE
description: The necklace pays tribute to an iconic code art of the exclusive DIOR BY ERL collaboration, the necklace features a silver-finish brass design adorned with a delicate play of white crystals for a sophisticated allure. An adjustable clasp enhanced by an openwork CD Icon signature and ERL signature medallion allows it to be worn at different lengths. The necklace can be paired with other DIOR BY ERL creations to complete the look.
